node.text: I am missing a bowl of good laksa. Need to check out who does islandwide delivery to satisfy my craving.
Won't be the same - but have you tried making it with Dancing Chef or Mekhala Living sauces?
@singaporeliciouz haha not a good cook like u
@sgfoodonfoot just get a ready paste!! I’m going to make laksa with ready paste too! Someone gifted me 😋
@sgfoodonfoot  yesterday i tried @huphup.co Laksa is pretty good!
